cdata.name: TattooCoin
cdata.desc: TattooCoin aims to be the cryptocurrency for the tattoo generation. Working towards partnering with tattoo shops and parlors that offer tattoo services and other merchants that tattooed and non-tattooed crypto people love, the dev team is taking altcoin and digital money from the trading sites to the actual world. A herculean task that would be achieved by taking baby steps towards the recognition of cryptocurrencies.
